A yellow crime-scene ribbon has cordoned off entrance one of East Rand Mall following Monday afternoon’s shooting JOHANNESBURG - Police and emergency services are on the scene of a shooting at East Rand Mall in Boksburg on Monday. Five men fled the scene in a white car. A yellow crime-scene ribbon has cordoned off entrance one of East Rand Mall following Monday afternoon’s shooting Eyewitnesses say the suspects sped off from the parking lot after the shooting. It’s understood the suspects were targeting a jewellery store in the mall. #EastRandMall Eyewitnesses say five men opened fire earlier this afternoon. Police on the scene are yet to confirm whether there were any injuries. AK pic.twitter.com/Xh3JVf4Sbk 